PN,42401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FA man from Wearside says he has been
OL,7,Fleft in constant pain after operations
OL,8,Fby a surgeon he once regarded as being
OL,9,F"like a god".
OL,11,FDavid Render had a series of
OL,12,Fprocedures to his hands and lower
OL,13,Farms, performed by consultant
OL,14,Forthopaedic surgeon Leslie Irwin.
OL,16,FThey were carried out for the NHS at a
OL,17,Fprivately run hospital in Washington
OL,18,Frun by Spire Healthcare.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FSpire has since apologised to Mr
OL,7,FRender and removed Mr Irwin's right to
OL,8,Fpractice at all its sites.
OL,10,FMr Render's case dates back to 2017
OL,11,Fwhen he sought medical attention after
OL,12,Fa fall.
OL,14,FDuring the process, he was referred,
OL,15,Fvia the NHS, to the Spire Washington
OL,16,FHospital.
OL,18,FAfter an initial procedure, Mr Render
OL,19,Fwas transferred to the care of Mr
OL,20,FIrwin.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FOver the next four years, Mr Irwin
OL,7,Fcarried out a series of operations on
OL,8,Fthe patient's hands, wrists and elbows.
OL,10,FAt the time, Mr Render says he
OL,11,Fidolised his surgeon.
OL,13,F"I thought he was saving us", he said,
OL,14,Fadding, "I thought the man could walk
OL,15,Fon water, he was a lovely bloke."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FSuch was Mr Render's faith in Mr
OL,7,FIrwin, he was not concerned when Spire
OL,8,FHealthcare contacted him last year,
OL,9,Fexplaining it was seeking an
OL,10,Findependent review of his treatment
OL,11,Fand asking for his feedback in a
OL,12,Fquestionnaire.
OL,14,FThen at the end of 2025, Mr Render
OL,15,Fsays he was shocked to receive its
OL,16,Fconclusions.
OL,18,FAmong the findings, it said:
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FMr Render was once a keen
OL,7,Fphotographer, travelling to different
OL,8,Fparts of the world to satisfy what he
OL,9,Fdescribes as an "obsession" for taking
OL,10,Fpictures.
OL,12,FNow, he says, it is rare he can enjoy
OL,13,Fhis hobby due to the pain and
OL,14,Frestricted movement that he lives with
OL,15,Fevery day.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FMr Render explained: "It's made my
OL,7,Flife very complicated because if I
OL,8,Fwant to do anything now I've got to
OL,9,Fplan ahead and everything I do comes
OL,10,Fwith a consequence because of the
OL,11,Fpain."
OL,13,FTo combat the pain caused by physical
OL,14,Factivity, Mr Render says he requires
OL,15,Fstrong painkillers.
OL,17,FEven so, he says he finds it difficult
OL,18,Fto sleep.
OL,26,@nD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FHe said: "A lot of the time I'm just
OL,7,Freading all night long because I can't
OL,8,Fsleep because I can't get comfortable."
OL,10,FMr Render's case is now in the hands
OL,11,Fof solicitors.
OL,13,FThe legal firm involved says other
OL,14,Fpatients who were treated by Leslie
OL,15,FIrwin are coming forward, anxious
OL,16,Fabout their own treatments.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FJohn Lowther, a medical negligence
OL,7,Fsolicitor at the practice, Slater and
OL,8,FGordon, explained: "We know some have
OL,9,Fbeen contacted by Spire about issues
OL,10,Fthat have been raised, others are
OL,11,Faware in the media about concerns
OL,12,Fabout Mr Irwin's work."
OL,14,FMr Lowther added: "We're seeing trends
OL,15,Fof patients who are very concerned
OL,16,Fabout repeat surgeries and we're
OL,17,Fseeing trends of people who are
OL,18,Fconcerned about the types of surgery
OL,19,Fthat they've had."
OL,26,@{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FLeslie Irwin practised at Spire
OL,7,FWashington Hospital for more than
OL,8,Ftwenty years, according to Spire
OL,9,FHealthcare, which runs the unit.
OL,11,FIn a statement, a Spire Healthcare
OL,12,Fspokesperson told ITV Tyne Tees: "We
OL,13,Fsincerely apologise to those patients
OL,14,Fwho did not receive an appropriate
OL,15,Fstandard of care from Mr Leslie Irwin,
OL,16,Fa consultant orthopaedic surgeon who
OL,17,Fhas not practised at Spire Washington
OL,18,FHospital since 2023.
OL,26,@tD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,F"We are currently reviewing specific
OL,7,Fprocedures that were provided to a
OL,8,Fselect cohort of patients of Mr Irwin
OL,9,Fand are in direct contact with these
OL,10,Fpatients to offer support at what we
OL,11,Frecognise is a concerning time. The
OL,12,Freview is being run in accordance with
OL,13,FNHS England's National Quality Board:
OL,14,FRecall Framework, which Spire
OL,15,FHealthcare helped to develop.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,F"If any Spire Washington patients have
OL,7,Fquestions about the care provided by
OL,8,FMr Irwin, they can call 0191 720 3031
OL,9,For email spirepne@spirehealthcare.com
OL,10,Fand a member of the dedicated review
OL,11,Fteam will call them back."
OL,13,FLeslie Irwin is no longer registered
OL,14,Fto practice medicine.
OL,16,FAn entry on the General Medical
OL,17,FCouncil's website confirms he gave up
OL,18,Fhis registration in May 2025.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FThe GMC, which is responsible for
OL,7,Fupholding professional standards, can
OL,8,Fonly investigate doctors who are
OL,9,Fregistered.
OL,11,FWe invited Mr Irwin to respond to the
OL,12,Fpoints raised in this report. He has
OL,13,Fnot provided a comment.
OL,15,FMr Irwin also worked within the NHS,
OL,16,Fat what is now South Tyneside and
OL,17,FSunderland NHS Foundation Trust.
OL,19,FThe trust told ITV Tyne Tees that Mr
OL,20,FIrwin retired in May 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FIn a statement, it said: "We are
OL,7,Fliaising with Spire in relation to
OL,8,Fconcerns over Mr Leslie Irwin and
OL,9,Fcurrently working through the detail
OL,10,Fof which patients the trust will need
OL,11,Fto review.
OL,13,F"We have also asked the Royal College
OL,14,Fof Surgeons to support us in this
OL,15,Fprocess. As part of this review, we
OL,16,Fwill be in touch with any former
OL,17,Fpatients directly and as a matter of
OL,18,Fpriority.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,F"Any former patients of Mr Irwin who
OL,7,Fdo have any questions or concerns can
OL,8,Fcontact the trust directly via
OL,9,Ffreephone 0800 587 6513 or email:
OL,10,Fstsft.adviceandcomplaints@nhs. net."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the healthcare regulator,
OL,13,Fthe Care Quality Commission (CQC),
OL,14,Fcarried out an inspection of surgery
OL,15,Fservices at the Spire in October 2025
OL,16,Fafter receiving concerns about the
OL,17,Fquality of care being provided.
OL,19,FThe findings will be published in due
OL,20,Fcourse though no date has yet been
OL,21,Fconfirmed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FOverall, the hospital is currently
OL,7,Frated as 'Good' though the outcome of
OL,8,Fthis latest inspection could influence
OL,9,Fthat rating.
OL,11,FFormer patient David Render says that
OL,12,Fafter putting his trust in Leslie
OL,13,FIrwin he is trying to understand
OL,14,Feverything he has now learned about
OL,15,Fhis treatment.
OL,17,F"He was," said Mr Render, "such a nice
OL,18,Fman you just believed he was doing
OL,19,Fthings to help you personally so I
OL,20,Fnever questioned him for a minute."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772467873
OL,3,CPatient who thought his surgeon could
OL,4,C'walk on water' now looking for answers
OL,6,FHe says the consequences of his
OL,7,Foperations have impacted every aspect
OL,8,Fof his life.
OL,10,FFor him, a priority is discovering how
OL,11,Fprocedures he thought were helping
OL,12,Fhim, went so badly wrong.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G16/16
